## 🐛 Bug Reports

### BUG-01 — Cart not saved after re-login

| Field | Details |
|-------|---------|
| **ID** | BUG-01 |
| **Title** | Cart items disappear after logout and login |
| **Severity** | High |
| **Priority** | High |
| **Status** | Open |
| **Environment** | Chrome 120, Windows 10 |
| **Reported by** | QA Engineer |

**Steps to Reproduce:**
1. Login to ShopEasy
2. Add any product to cart
3. Logout
4. Login again
5. Open cart

**Expected Result:** Cart should contain previously added items

**Actual Result:** Cart is empty after re-login

**Screenshot:** *(attached)*

