### BUG-02 — Price not updated when changing quantity

| Field | Details |
|-------|---------|
| **ID** | BUG-02 |
| **Title** | Total price does not recalculate when quantity is changed manually |
| **Severity** | Medium |
| **Priority** | Medium |
| **Status** | Open |
| **Environment** | Firefox 121, Windows 10 |

**Steps to Reproduce:**
1. Add product to cart
2. Open cart
3. Manually type quantity (e.g. "5") instead of using +/- buttons
4. Click outside the field

**Expected Result:** Total price updates to quantity × unit price

**Actual Result:** Total price stays unchanged

